com.oracle.tools.deferred
Class DeferredMatch<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.oracle.tools.deferred.DeferredMatch<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Deferred<Boolean>
public class DeferredMatch<T>
extends Object
implements Deferred<Boolean>

A DeferredMatch is a Deferred that represents a Hamcrest Matcher, that of which must be satisfied for a specified Deferred object at some point in the future.

A DeferredMatch will only return true when the match is successful, otherwise null will be returned.
